channel.title: Did I Jar My Client Wrong?
channel.description: K I have JARMaker and know how to do all the stuff but when I run the .JAR file I created, it just creates lots of empty files like "nullmain_file_cache.dat" and "nullmain_file_cache.idx" What am I doing wrong?

item.title: Did I Jar My Client Wrong?
item.dc:creator: @CreatorAlex CreatorAlex
item.description:
@CreatorAlex wrote:

Your client is trying to download your cache, but it’s not finding the files.

Check your cache path and see that you zipped the cache correctly. (And have it hosted on the web)
